{"tid":747124,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(廢老惡習之一) 喺超市買梳香蕉都衰撚過人","createTime":"2018-07-18T06:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T07:07:20.000Z","uid":54337,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d32f685c5b59badd1d7e0b04b51c214e43a80d","tid":747124,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"明明一梳蕉有八隻，<br />\n班廢老模過，發現其中一兩隻唔太靚，<br />\n係都要多手，搣走個一兩隻。<br />\n只買六隻。<br />\n大佬，你搣左出嚟個一兩隻，單丁，放埋一兩邊，一定無人買，真係好撚自私。<br />\n<br />\n搣搣搣，我真係好好奇，你班廢老究竟搣乜撚野？"},{"pid":"0323734e474625f23b92fd931de05722917cb9d7","tid":747124,"uid":57844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:34:51.000Z","msg":"我成日執果D 一兩隻果D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87200c7255ec7161a24b94bbde3a678ce1b8dff","tid":747124,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:35:30.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n我樓下果間都係咁<br />\n結果剩番D一兩隻既蕉出黎<br />\n仆街廢老"},{"pid":"3b1810d3cfdf45f7dce56555e08a89ae1f6e2ca9","tid":747124,"uid":138420,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:35:56.000Z","msg":"下 正常野黎 樓主無出街買過野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95cdbff6cf0e914e2dd01bebf07495ffcecf592a","tid":747124,"uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:36:25.000Z","msg":"買梳蕉就睇到：廢老 = 自私"},{"pid":"9239ea988cc86a8f0e446215b35f17b6553ef9ad","tid":747124,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:36:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccd3c633b378ab495b2ebce88dad15e8ac38fd38","tid":747124,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:37:56.000Z","msg":"咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad13c166884abbc8026db908c1585b9997a302ab","tid":747124,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:38:49.000Z","msg":"唔靚果兩隻無人會買唔係天公地道既事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32495627b084a212ccb0d5d8fe8c2b51e955359a","tid":747124,"uid":107269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:39:01.000Z","msg":"邊個話唔可咁做ga?"},{"pid":"61874b26128e1080ef85948ba2a82186dfb7be39","tid":747124,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:39:27.000Z","msg":"冇搣爛我覺得冇所謂喎<br />\n我有時見佢太大梳食唔哂都會搣<br />\n有d求其搣搣到爛哂 搞到唔食得就衰姐"},{"pid":"f483d718b91ea226cbff3181cbc4ae271aee6b75","tid":747124,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本應該PACK撚好曬佢 唔可以俾人搣<br />\n但要分返幾隻幾隻咁 好多時都食唔到一梳<br />\n<br />\n廢老搣剩個啲最後 就會執埋一包減價賤賣"},{"pid":"15a8b7da96e3aca833f5300f7da8a215068aafdd","tid":747124,"uid":52942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"我有個習慣，一次只可以買四條，多一定食唔哂，我中意散執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b04aaff65b85dd87168a5d47106c67801b9016","tid":747124,"uid":34336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:43:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82da96a365bc4c2260ee15886685744b22c2a7ee","tid":747124,"uid":138420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90b04aaff65b85dd87168a5d47106c67801b9016","tid":747124,"uid":34336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3b1810d3cfdf45f7dce56555e08a89ae1f6e2ca9","tid":747124,"uid":138420,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:35:56.000Z","msg":"下 正常野黎 樓主無出街買過野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:43:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"所以話道德撚真係On9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學子華神引用黃霑既名句 <br />\n為真小人爭取社會地位 不讓偽君子霸佔全世界"},{"pid":"9f25c3a22bfc9cbde9604c5543ae5689ad949140","tid":747124,"uid":29689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:54:27.000Z","msg":"真心問，其實係咪唔搣得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我自己唔鐘意食太熟嘅蕉<br />\n多數每次買3~4條<br />\n所以次次都係執人地搣出來散曬嗰啲<br />\n不過我又冇乜所謂嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非係撞到瘀曬嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0907663706eba02073b2670a9984c195b89916fa","tid":747124,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:07:20.000Z","msg":"香蕉呢單都算，叫有人接貨，有D廢老好賤，買榴槤可以狂用手指禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n想禁黎睇下熟唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到超市而家用硬盒裝榴槤，繼續禁啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}